GREENOCK now has superfast 4G mobile broadband. Town is in the fastlane GREENOCK now has superfast 4G mobile broadband.It's being supplied by EE - the world's biggest mobile phone provider - which has also introduced it to cutomers in Glasgow as well as the South Lanarkshire towns of East Kilbride and Hamilton.Cumbernauld in North Lanarkshire also has access to a superfast 4G network. 